    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Compare cost of living between two cities to find the salary you need to maintain your current standard of living.</p>

    <div data-controller="cost-of-living-calculator" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
